<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>서류 안내시스템</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: #f5f6f8; color: #1a1d23; font-size: 14px; }
  .app { padding: 8px; width: 100%; }
  .header { background: #1a1d23; color: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; }
  .header-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .header-icon { font-size: 24px; }
  .header h1 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; }
  .header p { font-size: 12px; color: #8b92a0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .header-actions { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .hbtn { padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 7px; border: 1.5px solid #3a3f4b; background: transparent; color: #c9cdd5; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; white-space: nowrap; }
  .hbtn:hover { border-color: #6366f1; color: #a5b4fc; }
  .hbtn.export { border-color: #059669; color: #6ee7b7; }
  .hbtn.export:hover { background: #065f46; }
  .hbtn.settings { border-color: #f59e0b; color: #fcd34d; }
  .hbtn.settings:hover { background: #78350f; }
  .hbtn.danger { border-color: #ef4444; color: #fca5a5; }
  .hbtn.danger:hover { background: #7f1d1d; }
  .layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }
  .panel { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; }
  .panel-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .panel-title-btn { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #6366f1; background: #eef2ff; border: none; border-radius: 5px; padding: 3px 8px; cursor: pointer; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0; }
  .panel-title-btn:hover { background: #e0e7ff; }

  /* 유형 버튼 */
  .type-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }
  .type-btn { padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; background: #fff; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #374151; transition: all 0.15s; text-align: left; }
  .type-btn:hover { border-color: #6366f1; color: #6366f1; }
  .type-btn.active { border-color: #6366f1; background: #eef2ff; color: #4f46e5; font-weight: 700; }

  /* 서류 목록 */
  .search-wrap { position: relative; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .search-input { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 32px 8px 34px; font-size: 12px; outline: none; transition: border 0.15s; font-family: inherit; background: #f9fafb; }
  .search-input:focus { border-color: #6366f1; background: #fff; }
  .search-icon { position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 14px; pointer-events: none; }
  .search-clear { position: absolute; right: 8px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; padding: 0; display: none; }
  .search-clear:hover { color: #6b7280; }
  .checklist { max-height: 360px; overflow-y: auto; }
  .no-result { text-align: center; padding: 28px 0; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; }
  /* 프리셋 */
  .preset-panel { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .preset-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 7px; margin-bottom: 10px; min-height: 34px; align-items: center; }
  .preset-empty { font-size: 12px; color: #c4c9d4; }
  .preset-chip { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 5px 10px 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; background: #eef2ff; border: 1.5px solid #c7d2fe; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #4f46e5; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .preset-chip:hover { background: #e0e7ff; border-color: #6366f1; }
  .chip-del { background: none; border: none; color: #a5b4fc; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; cursor: pointer; padding: 0 1px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .chip-del:hover { color: #ef4444; }
  .preset-save-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
  .preset-name-input { flex: 1; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 7px; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 12px; outline: none; transition: border 0.15s; font-family: inherit; }
  .preset-name-input:focus { border-color: #6366f1; }
  .preset-save-btn { background: #eef2ff; color: #4f46e5; border: 1.5px solid #c7d2fe; border-radius: 7px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; }
  .preset-save-btn:hover { background: #e0e7ff; }
  .category { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .category-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #4f46e5; background: #eef2ff; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .doc-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 6px; transition: background 0.1s; cursor: pointer; }
  .doc-item:hover { background: #eef2ff; }
  .doc-item:hover .doc-name { color: #4f46e5; }
  .doc-item:hover .doc-actions { opacity: 1; }
  .doc-item input[type="checkbox"] { margin-top: 3px; accent-color: #6366f1; cursor: pointer; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .doc-label { flex: 1; cursor: pointer; }
  .doc-name { font-size: 13px; color: #1a1d23; line-height: 1.4; }
  .doc-method { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 2px; }
  .doc-actions { display: flex; gap: 2px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.15s; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .doc-btn { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .doc-btn.edit:hover { background: #eef2ff; }
  .doc-btn.del:hover  { background: #fee2e2; }
  .doc-btn.move { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; }
  .doc-btn.move:hover { background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; }
  .doc-btn.move:disabled { opacity: 0.2; cursor: default; background: none; }
  .add-area { margin-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6; padding-top: 12px; }
  .add-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .add-input { flex: 1; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 7px; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 12px; outline: none; transition: border 0.15s; }
  .add-input:focus { border-color: #6366f1; }
  .add-select { border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 7px; padding: 7px 8px; font-size: 12px; outline: none; background: #fff; color: #374151; }
  .add-btn { background: #6366f1; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 7px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; }
  .add-btn:hover { background: #4f46e5; }

  /* 카톡 */
  .kakao-panel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .kakao-box { background: #f9e000; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; flex: 1; min-height: 300px; }
  .kakao-header { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1d23; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .kakao-bubble { background: #fff; border-radius: 4px 12px 12px 12px; padding: 14px; font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.9; color: #1a1d23; white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 260px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .kakao-empty { color: #aaa; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; }
  .action-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .copy-btn { flex: 1; background: #1a1d23; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 11px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .copy-btn:hover { background: #374151; }
  .copy-btn.copied { background: #059669; }
  .reset-btn { background: #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 11px 14px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; }
  .reset-btn:hover { background: #e5e7eb; }
  .count-badge { background: #6366f1; color: #fff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1px 7px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }

  /* 모달 공통 */
  .modal-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45); z-index: 200; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .modal-overlay.show { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
  .modal { background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; width: 460px; max-width: 90vw; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); max-height: 90vh; overflow-y: auto; }
  .modal-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1d23; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .modal-field { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .modal-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px; }
  .modal-label span { font-weight: 400; color: #9ca3af; text-transform: none; font-size: 10px; margin-left: 4px; }
  .modal-input { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 12px; font-size: 13px; outline: none; transition: border 0.15s; font-family: inherit; }
  .modal-input:focus { border-color: #6366f1; }
  .modal-textarea { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 12px; font-size: 13px; outline: none; font-family: inherit; resize: vertical; min-height: 70px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .modal-textarea:focus { border-color: #6366f1; }
  .modal-select { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 12px; font-size: 13px; outline: none; background: #fff; font-family: inherit; }
  .modal-actions { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .modal-save { flex: 1; background: #6366f1; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }
  .modal-save:hover { background: #4f46e5; }
  .modal-save.amber { background: #d97706; }
  .modal-save.amber:hover { background: #b45309; }
  .modal-cancel { background: #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; }
  .modal-cancel:hover { background: #e5e7eb; }
  .info-preview { background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 8px; border: 1px dashed #e5e7eb; }
  .info-preview b { color: #4f46e5; }

  /* 유형 관리 목록 */
  .type-manage-list { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .type-manage-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; margin-bottom: 6px; background: #fff; }
  .type-manage-item:hover { border-color: #c7d2fe; background: #f8f8ff; }
  .type-emoji { font-size: 16px; width: 24px; text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .type-manage-name { flex: 1; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #1a1d23; }
  .type-manage-actions { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
  .tm-btn { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .tm-btn.edit:hover { background: #eef2ff; }
  .tm-btn.del:hover { background: #fee2e2; }
  .type-add-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-top: 6px; }
  .emoji-input { width: 52px; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 7px; padding: 7px 8px; font-size: 14px; outline: none; text-align: center; }
  .emoji-input:focus { border-color: #6366f1; }
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6; margin: 14px 0; }

  .toast { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; padding: 11px 18px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; pointer-events: none; z-index: 300; }
  .toast.green { background: #059669; color: #fff; }
  .toast.blue { background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; }
  .toast.amber { background: #d97706; color: #fff; }
  .toast.show { opacity: 1; }
  #fileInput { display: none; }

  /* 관리자/직원 모드 */
  .staff-only { display: none !important; }
  .admin-mode .staff-only { display: flex !important; }
  .admin-mode .staff-only-block { display: block !important; }
  .staff-only-block { display: none !important; }
  .mode-badge { padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; border: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .mode-badge.staff { background: #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; }
  .mode-badge.admin { background: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; }
  /* 비밀번호 모달 */
  .pw-modal { background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; width: 320px; max-width: 90vw; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); text-align: center; }
  .pw-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .pw-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1d23; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pw-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .pw-input { width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 15px; outline: none; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 4px; font-family: inherit; transition: border 0.15s; }
  .pw-input:focus { border-color: #6366f1; }
  .pw-input.error { border-color: #ef4444; animation: shake 0.3s; }
  .pw-btn { width: 100%; background: #6366f1; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 11px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px; }
  .pw-btn:hover { background: #4f46e5; }
  .pw-err { font-size: 12px; color: #ef4444; margin-top: 8px; min-height: 18px; }
  @keyframes shake { 0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)} 25%{transform:translateX(-6px)} 75%{transform:translateX(6px)} }

  .fmt-btns { display:flex; gap:4px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .fmt-btn { padding:3px 9px; border:1.5px solid #c9a800; border-radius:5px; background:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#8b6914; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.15s; }
  .fmt-btn:hover { background:#fef3c7; }
  .fmt-btn.active { background:#f9e000; border-color:#b8a000; color:#1a1d23; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #e5e7eb; border-radius: 4px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<input type="file" id="fileInput" accept=".json" onchange="importDocs(event)">
<input type="file" id="pdfViewInput" accept=".pdf" onchange="loadPdfView(event)" style="position:fixed;left:-9999px;visibility:hidden;">

<div class="app" id="appDiv">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-left">
      <div class="header-icon">📋</div>
      <div>
        <h1>준비서류 안내 시스템</h1>
        <p id="headerSub">유형 선택 → 서류 체크 → 카톡 메시지 복사</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-actions">
      <button class="hbtn settings" onclick="openSettings()">⚙️ 설정</button>
      <button class="hbtn staff-only" onclick="document.getElementById('fileInput').click()">📂 불러오기</button>
      <button class="hbtn danger staff-only" onclick="openResetModal()">🔄 초기화</button>
      <button class="hbtn export staff-only" onclick="exportDocs()">💾 저장하기</button>
      <button class="mode-badge staff" id="modeBadge" onclick="onModeBadgeClick()">🔒 직원 모드</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <input type="file" id="pdfViewInput" accept=".pdf" style="position:fixed;left:-9999px;visibility:hidden;" onchange="loadPdfView(event)">

  <div class="layout">
    <!-- PDF 뷰어 컬럼 -->
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;min-height:0;">
      <input type="file" id="pdfViewInput" accept=".pdf" style="display:none;" onchange="loadPdfView(event)">
      <div style="background:#1a1d23;border-radius:10px 10px 0 0;">
        <!-- 탭 목록 -->
        <div id="pdfTabBar" style="display:none;padding:6px 8px 0;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;"></div>
        <!-- 툴바 -->
        <!-- 즐겨찾기 목록 -->
        <div id="pdfFavBar" style="padding:0 8px 6px;display:none;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #2d3139;"></div>
        <div style="padding:8px 10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;">
          <span style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#9ca3af;">📄 PDF</span>
          <div style="flex:1;"></div>
          <button id="pdfFavBtn" onclick="togglePdfFav()" title="즐겨찾기 등록" style="display:none;font-size:11px;padding:3px 8px;border:1.5px solid #3a3f4b;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;color:#fbbf24;font-weight:600;">☆ 등록</button>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;background:#2d3139;border-radius:6px;padding:2px 6px;" id="pdfZoomCtrl" style="display:none;">
            <button onclick="pdfZoom(-10)" style="width:20px;height:20px;border:none;background:#3a3f4b;color:#fff;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;">−</button>
            <span id="pdfZoomLabel" style="font-size:11px;color:#c9cdd5;font-weight:600;min-width:32px;text-align:center;">100%</span>
            <button onclick="pdfZoom(10)" style="width:20px;height:20px;border:none;background:#3a3f4b;color:#fff;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;">+</button>
          </div>
          <label for="pdfViewInput" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border:1.5px solid #3a3f4b;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;color:#c9cdd5;font-weight:600;">📂 열기</label>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="pdfIframeWrap" style="background:#525659;border-radius:0 0 10px 10px;min-height:500px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden;">
        <div id="pdfEmpty" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:12px;color:#9ca3af;">
          <span style="font-size:36px;">📄</span>
          <div style="font-size:12px;text-align:center;">PDF 파일을 열어주세요</div>
          <label for="pdfViewInput" style="padding:8px 18px;background:#6366f1;color:#fff;border-radius:7px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;">📂 열기</label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="preset-panel">
        <div class="panel-title" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
          <span>⭐ 즐겨찾기 프리셋</span>
        </div>
        <div class="preset-list" id="presetList">
          <span class="preset-empty">저장된 프리셋이 없어요. 서류를 추가한 후 저장해 보세요!</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:4px;">
          <button class="preset-save-btn" onclick="openDocPresetModal()" style="flex:1;">📋 서류 프리셋 추가</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
        <div class="panel-title">
          <span>의뢰인 유형</span>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;" class="staff-only">
            <button class="panel-title-btn" onclick="openCatManager()">📂 카테고리</button>
            <button class="panel-title-btn" onclick="openTypeManager()">✏️ 유형 관리</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="type-grid" id="typeGrid"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-title">
          <span>서류 목록</span>
          <span class="count-badge" id="checkedCount">0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="search-wrap">
          <span class="search-icon">🔍</span>
          <input class="search-input" id="searchInput" placeholder="서류명 또는 발급방법 검색..." oninput="onSearch(this.value)" />
          <button class="search-clear" id="searchClear" onclick="clearSearch()">×</button>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist" id="checklist"></div>
        <div class="add-area staff-only-block">
          <div class="add-row">
            <select class="add-select" id="addCategory">
              <option value="공통서류">공통</option>
              <option value="재산현황">재산</option>
              <option value="수입">수입</option>
              <option value="진술서">진술서</option>
              <option value="부채서류">부채</option>
            </select>
            <select class="add-select" id="addType"></select>
          </div>
          <div class="add-row">
            <input class="add-input" id="addName" placeholder="서류명 입력" />
          </div>
          <div class="add-row">
            <input class="add-input" id="addMethod" placeholder="발급방법 (예: 정부24 앱)" />
            <button class="add-btn" onclick="addCustomDoc()">+ 추가</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel kakao-panel">
      <div class="panel-title">카톡 메시지 미리보기</div>

